.SH "CONFIGURATION"
.SS "Location"
.sp
pasfetch searches for a configuration in the following places:
1. $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/pasfetch/config.ini
2. $HOME/.pasfetch.ini
3. /etc/pasfetch.ini
.SS "Configuring"
.sp
